{"tid":6613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友第一次去旅行…","createTime":"2016-11-27T12:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T13:29:26.000Z","uid":25374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1673df9e68e1a77f78cefb607bc01f0323954aaa","tid":6613,"uid":25374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"上年公司黎左個新同事,<br />\n幾斯文有少少似方大x個type&hellip;<br />\n咁相處落都幾開心,,叫做互有好感啦..<br />\n一個月前正式一齊左!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個人好乖既,加埋我屋企係家教好嚴個種,<br />\n所以我地一直都係發乎情止乎禮&hellip;冇咩咩過...<br />\n我地上星期拎左大假&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打算下年去日本浸溫泉玩番幾日,<br />\n順便過我地既第一個半年...<br />\n其實都預左到時可能會有再進一步既發展嫁啦&hellip;<br />\n但我驚佢會嫌棄我既身材...<br />\n話就話我個波都幾大(有c-d左右),<br />\n但副乳問題都幾嚴重,所以我夏天都唔敢著背心&hellip;<br />\n而家有少少擔心,唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2574d411b70d66261521315a0de924fd5926abb","tid":6613,"uid":22533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.giphy.com/media/i8WeOWs3EYmmk/giphy.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fi8WeOWs3EYmmk%2Fgiphy.gif%20&h=0b92a89a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"394d7777e00d94d048d4badf49c074a5c77fcc36","tid":6613,"uid":8329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/i8WeOWs3EYmmk/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fi8WeOWs3EYmmk%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6b043b9c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2f7cc7930d3b7b09ce8e0be5dcdab7ff252af8","tid":6613,"uid":29144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"收兵post"},{"pid":"f147ff52fbb572a70695120f9021e82d30fc3d25","tid":6613,"u